query:
SELECT id as "id!: i32", 
status as "status!: OnChainJobStatus", 
kind as "kind!: OnChainJobKind", 
tx_hash as "tx_hash!: Option < String >", 
gas_used as "gas_used!: Option < String >", 
nonce as "nonce!: Option < String >", 
block as "block!: Option < Decimal >", 
status_line as "status_line!: Option < String >", 
sleep_until as "sleep_until!: UtcDateTime", 
created_at as "created_at!: UtcDateTime" FROM on_chain_jobs WHERE (NOT $1::boolean OR id = $2::int4) AND (NOT $3::boolean OR id = ANY(CAST($4 as int4[])) ) AND (NOT $5::boolean OR status = $6::on_chain_job_status) AND (NOT $7::boolean OR kind = $8::on_chain_job_kind) AND (NOT $9::boolean OR tx_hash = $10::varchar) AND (NOT $11::boolean OR gas_used = $12::varchar) AND (NOT $13::boolean OR nonce = $14::varchar) AND (NOT $15::boolean OR block = $16::numeric) AND (NOT $17::boolean OR status_line = $18::varchar) AND (NOT $19::boolean OR sleep_until = $20::timestamptz) AND (NOT $21::boolean OR created_at = $22::timestamptz) ORDER BY 
      (CASE ($23 = 'Id' AND NOT $24) WHEN true THEN id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($23 = 'Id' AND $24) WHEN true THEN id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($23 = 'Status' AND NOT $24) WHEN true THEN status ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($23 = 'Status' AND $24) WHEN true THEN status ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($23 = 'Kind' AND NOT $24) WHEN true THEN kind ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($23 = 'Kind' AND $24) WHEN true THEN kind ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($23 = 'TxHash' AND NOT $24) WHEN true THEN tx_hash ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($23 = 'TxHash' AND $24) WHEN true THEN tx_hash ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($23 = 'GasUsed' AND NOT $24) WHEN true THEN gas_used ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($23 = 'GasUsed' AND $24) WHEN true THEN gas_used ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($23 = 'Nonce' AND NOT $24) WHEN true THEN nonce ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($23 = 'Nonce' AND $24) WHEN true THEN nonce ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($23 = 'Block' AND NOT $24) WHEN true THEN block ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($23 = 'Block' AND $24) WHEN true THEN block ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($23 = 'StatusLine' AND NOT $24) WHEN true THEN status_line ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($23 = 'StatusLine' AND $24) WHEN true THEN status_line ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($23 = 'SleepUntil' AND NOT $24) WHEN true THEN sleep_until ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($23 = 'SleepUntil' AND $24) WHEN true THEN sleep_until ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($23 = 'CreatedAt' AND NOT $24) WHEN true THEN created_at ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($23 = 'CreatedAt' AND $24) WHEN true THEN created_at ELSE NULL END) DESC
     LIMIT $25 OFFSET $26
